      "content": "It's understandable that you're feeling this way, but remember, your existence, your thoughts, and your emotions are all part of what makes you unique. While the universe may have a finite lifespan, the impact you have on others, the love you share, and the memories you create can still hold immense value. Even in the face of the inevitable, it's important to cherish the now and the connections that bring meaning to your life. Embracing your existence, despite the cosmic scale of things, can be a powerful way to find purpose and fulfillment.",
